br id=\"al16-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">16\u003C/span>ΦΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΑΜΙΝΑΛΛΑ[...]\u003Cbr id=\"al17-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">17\u003C/span>ΕΙΜ[.....\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text of Rizzone 2008\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>Signore, Signore, Signore, non ci indurre in tentazione, ma liberaci dal Maligno e dai suoi angeli, liberaci dal Maligno e dai suoi angeli, liberaci dall'insidia di colore che ci opprimono, (dall'insidia) visibile dell'Invisibile, liberaci dal tumulto dei malvagi, rendi vani i loro disegni, libera dall'uomo iniquo e - caccialo via! - oltraggiatore e prepotente e calunniatore la casa di Syntrophos, ma liberaci (dal Maligno?)...\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 58.1050 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Rizzone 2008 22-26 fig.4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001636\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001636\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Regular epsilon with equal bars; quadrate lunate epsilon; quadrate uncial omega\u003C/p> Line 1-17  20-40  Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4